<SYNC Start=7207><P Class=ENCC>
Terry, I know I haven't worked here<br>very long but would it be possible...
<SYNC Start=12338><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=12545><P Class=ENCC>
...if I got a $1 00 advance<br>on my salary?
