<SYNC Start=558257><P Class=ENCC>
Hi.
<SYNC Start=559588><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=560726><P Class=ENCC>
-We used to work together.<br>-We did?
<SYNC Start=563456><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=563663><P Class=ENCC>
Yeah, at Macy's.<br>You' re the Obsession girl, right?
<SYNC Start=567224><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=567433><P Class=ENCC>
-Yes.<br>-I was the Aramis guy.
<SYNC Start=570425><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=571404><P Class=ENCC>
-Aramis. Aramis. Aramis.<br>-Yeah, right!
<SYNC Start=576341><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=577276><P Class=ENCC>
-You' re the best in the business.<br>-Get out.
<SYNC Start=580643><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=580846><P Class=ENCC>
You' re amazing! You know when<br>to spritz. You know when to lay back.
<SYNC Start=585874><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=586085><P Class=ENCC>
Really? You don't know<br>what that means to me.
<SYNC Start=589953><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=591991><P Class=ENCC>
