Nothing.
<SYNC Start=598454><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=607640><P Class=ENCC>
-Listen, do you wanna go get a drink?<br>-Yeah, that would be
<SYNC Start=613135><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=614380><P Class=ENCC>
-What's wrong?<br>-I have to do something.
<SYNC Start=617975><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=618184><P Class=ENCC>
What?
<SYNC Start=619583><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=621988><P Class=ENCC>
-Leave.<br>-Wait, wait, wait!
<SYNC Start=625788><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=668334><P Class=ENCC>
So I guess you all saw it.
<SYNC Start=670564><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=670770><P Class=ENCC>
-What?<br>-Saw what?
<SYNC Start=672101><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=672304><P Class=ENCC>
No, we' re just laughing. You know<br>how laughter can be infectious.
<SYNC Start=677037><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=695895><P Class=ENCC>
Set another place for Thanksgiving.<br>My entire family thinks I have VD.
<SYNC Start=700992><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
