<SYNC Start=738896><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=739105><P Class=ENCC>
-Oh, you must stop shooping.<br>-Okay, l' m gonna get my stuff.
<SYNC Start=743599><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=743809><P Class=ENCC>
Will you come in?
<SYNC Start=745333><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=745544><P Class=ENCC>
I prefer to keep a safe distance<br>from all this merriment.
<SYNC Start=749776><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
