Look out! Incoming pumpkin pie!
<SYNC Start=753509><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=759859><P Class=ENCC>
We laughed when you did it with<br>the stuffing, but that's not funny.
<SYNC Start=764523><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=765164><P Class=ENCC>
Hey, Monica, I got a question.<br>I don't see any T ator T ots.
<SYNC Start=769498><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=769702><P Class=ENCC>
-That's not a question.<br>-My mom makes them. It's a tradition.
<SYNC Start=774298><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=774507><P Class=ENCC>
