<SYNC Start=818043><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=818250><P Class=ENCC>
I thought we could have them whipped<br>and then add some peas and onions.
<SYNC Start=823483><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=823689><P Class=ENCC>
Why do that?
<SYNC Start=825054><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=825257><P Class=ENCC>
Because then they'd be just like my<br>mom used to make it, before she died.
<SYNC Start=830422><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=832131><P Class=ENCC>
Okay. Three kinds<br>of potatoes coming up.
<SYNC Start=835999><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
